RNSClientHome
public abstract class BaseClient
extends java.lang.Object

Web service client APIs for Globus. Improved org.globus.wsrf.client.BaseClient. This object can be created(initialized) many times. (org.globus.wsrf.client.BaseClient cannot be created many times.)
